summary.text: URGENT: Customer Mike Thompson called from Highway 401 near Mississauga. His 2018 Ford F-150 has a flat tire and he's stranded on the shoulder. Customer sounds stressed but is in a safe location behind the guardrail. He needs immediate roadside assistance or emergency tire service. Vehicle is a work truck and he has important deliveries scheduled. Customer mentioned he doesn't have a spare tire that's road-worthy.
